{
  "stem": "1753.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 109.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "How did you know that there were gas chambers in Treblinka?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You just know and you sense.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And if you didn't know, if you only speculated when you were sitting there, and when you got there a few days later, for sure you learned what was going on.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Certain things you just know, you sense, you feel.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there's gossip, and there's conversation, you know, gossip, conversation, when speculation becomes reality.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So in any case, so including-- and that Treblinka I, that penal camp, was divided into [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] four sections.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Barrack B-- I don't know why they call it Barrack B, but Barrack B was where the prisoners, the real-- the-- the-- the-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the experienced people, the-- the carpenters, the people that had a trade, that had trades that the Germans could use for whatever their need, for whatever they needed to do.",
      "word_count": 57
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "These were the people in Barrack B.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In fact, there were families, husbands, wives, and children.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I would estimate maybe about 200 people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then there was Barrack A.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That's where we were when we arrived, commingled with the others.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There must have been about 3,000 workers.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "These were the black workers that performed the kind of work that the professionals [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] wouldn't do because they were to important for the Germans.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They needed them for the other reasons.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So and then there was Barrack [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] C, where the Poles, the Aryans, the Christian Poles, for whatever reason, they had to be there because of some crimes that in the German eyes they had committed, for not-- you know, that they had to-- for the certain contingent of their--",
      "word_count": 53
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The farmers were there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They didn't give enough corn.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
